BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:Pz0Av79hy2VC1UJKAUh9w
SUMMARY:Free Introductory Improv Class ISSAQUAH
DTSTAMP:20260214T003616Z
DTSTART:20260215T110000Z
DESCRIPTION:Have you always wanted to take an improv class\\\, but weren’t 
	sure if you want to commit to a quarter-long term? We have the solution. J
	oin us in Seattle on 2/20 at 7:00pm\\n\\n\\n\\n✨ Ever Thought About Trying
	 Improv… But Weren’t Sure Where to Start? ✨ \\nTotally get it—jumping into
	 something new can feel a lot. That’s why we’re hooking you up with a FREE
	 Intro to Improv Class made just for folks who are curious\\\, kinda nervo
	us\\\, or just wanna try something different. 👀 \\n\\n\\nHave you always w
	anted to take an improv class\\\, but weren’t sure if you wanted to commit
	 to a quarter-long term? We have the solution. Join us in ISSAQUAH at our 
	new eastside improv school \\n✨ Ever Thought About Trying Improv… But Were
	n’t Sure Where to Start? ✨ \\nTotally get it—jumping into something new ca
	n feel a lot. That’s why we’re hooking you up with a FREE Intro to Improv 
	Class made just for folks who are curious\\\, kinda nervous\\\, or just wa
	nna try something different. 👀 \\nNo experience? No stress. This class is 
	100% beginner-friendly. Like\\\, truly. We’re talking zero pressure\\\, ma
	jor good vibes. \\nAt Unexpected Productions—Seattle’s biggest & boldest i
	mprov school—we believe everyone has a creative spark. Whether you wanna l
	evel up your communication game\\\, shake up your routine\\\, or just laug
	h for two hours straight with cool strangers\\\, we got you. 💥 \\n🧠 You’ll
	 learn how to stay in the moment\\\, trust your instincts\\\, and say “yes
	\\\, and…” to life\\n🎭 You’ll be guided by pros who make it all feel easy\
	\\, welcoming\\\, and seriously fun\\n👯‍♀️ You’ll meet awesome people and may
	be even surprise yourself \\nBut heads up: we’re only offering 50 spots—an
	d these go fast. So if your gut’s like “do ittt\\\,” listen to it. 😉 \\n📅 
	Date: Sunday\\\, Feb. 15\\\, 2026\\n🕒 Time: 11:00am – 1:00pm\\n📍 Location:
	 Improv School Eastside Issaquah 1315 NW Mall Street\\\, Suite 4 Issaquah\
	\\, WA 98027 (next to the Gaslamp Bar & Grill)\\n👥 Ages: 18+\\n💸 Cost: $0.
	00 (yup\\\, totally free)\\n🎯 Prerequisite: No improv experience needed\\n
	🚨 Max spots: 40 (Our regular classes are smaller\\\, btw—12–16 students) \
	\n✨ Ready to play\\\, explore\\\, and let go a little?\\nSpots are limited
	\\\, so snag yours now and come see what the Unexpected is all about. \\n\
	\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nRegister Here\n\nFrom Unexpected Productio
	ns
URL:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/f/
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions Improv School ISSAQUAH/EASTSIDE\\\, 1315 NW
	 Mall Street\\\, Suite 4\\\, Issaquah\\\, WA\\\, 98108\\\, United States
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
