	 Saturday at 7:30 PM\\\, our talented performers take the quirkiest\\\, sw
	eetest\\\, and most outrageous listings and imagine what happens when thes
	e almost-lovers actually go on a date…and beyond. \\nWhether you’re a hope
	less romantic or a hardened cynic\\\, you’ll laugh\\\, cringe\\\, and mayb
	e even tear up as we explore the eternal question: is fantasy really bette
	r than reality? Join us for a night of unexpected twists\\\, unfiltered hi
	larity\\\, and a dash of love-inspired chaos.\n\nFrom Unexpected Productio
	ns
