UID:EooKnSjwxOlLPSsm_8mHO
SUMMARY:Black Ice: An American Sitcom Improvised
DTSTAMP:20260214T003616Z
DTSTART:20260222T190000Z
DESCRIPTION:Welcome to our live studio audience! Be a part of an improvised
	 television sitcom in the style of Norman Lear.\\n\\n\\n\\nOur talented im
	provisers will use your suggestions to create an unforgettable show that w
	ill have you laughing out loud. Norman Lear was a legendary producer and w
	riter of popular 1970s sitcoms such as All in the Family\\\, Maude\\\, The
	 Jeffersons\\\, and Good Times. His shows were known for introducing polit
	ical and social themes to the sitcom format. As our audience\\\, you have 
	the important role of providing the laugh track and suggestions to make th
	is show a success. So let’s work together to create a hilarious American S
	itcom that will be talked about for years to come!\n\nFrom Unexpected Prod
	uctions
URL:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/black-ice-an-american-sitco
	m-improvised/2026-02-22/
